tests.name: consent_test
tests.run: if (find . -type f -name "*.txt" -exec grep -q "I acknowledge" {} \;) &>/dev/null; then exit 0; else exit 1; fi

tests.name: photo_test
tests.run: if (find . -type f \( -name "*.jpg" -o -name "*.jpeg" -o -name "*.png" \)) &>/dev/null; then exit 0; else exit 1; fi
